title: [Evermore Hollow, River Entry]
description: Towering trees form a canopy of dark shadows over the small landing, their gentle rustling creating avenues of illumination where the twilight-kissed sky can filter through.  Pulled back from the reach of the frolicking waters, a bunch of lantern-lit gondolas rest in cleaved lines that part the grass.  Tiny lanterns filled with will-o'-wisps flicker wildly, their dancing lights illuminating an uneven luminescent azure stone path.
